                        in their infancy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="span2">
                    @*<img class="IMGFullSize" src="../../Content/images/add3.png" />*@
                     @Model.position4
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span3">
            @*<img class="IMGFullSize" src="../../Content/images/add1.png" />*@
